    "faq_glowrelief": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "display_id": false,
        "visibility": "always-display",
        "custom_liquid": "<style>.faq-wrap{max-width:780px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px;}.faq-header{text-align:center;margin-bottom:32px;}.faq-caption{font-size:1.3rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:8px;}.faq-title{font-size:3.2rem;font-weight:700;color:#111;line-height:1.2;margin:0 0 32px;}.faq-item{border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.2);border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:12px;transition:background 0.3s;}.faq-item:hover{background:rgba(0,0,0,0.03);cursor:pointer;}.faq-item summary{display:flex;width:100%;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:18px 24px;position:relative;list-style:none;}.faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none;}.faq-q{color:#111;padding-right:36px;}.faq-icon{width:22px;height:22px;min-width:22px;fill:#111;position:absolute;right:24px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);transition:transform 0.3s;}.faq-item[open] .faq-icon{transform:translateY(-50%) rotate(180deg);}.faq-answer{padding:0 24px 20px;color:#333;line-height:1.6;}.faq-cta{text-align:center;margin-top:32px;}.faq-btn{display:inline-block;padding:16px 40px;background:#111;color:#fff;font-size:1.5rem;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;}@media(max-width:768px){.faq-btn{display:block;text-align:center;}}</style><div class=\"faq-wrap\"><div class=\"faq-header\"><h2 class=\"faq-title pp-font-semibold\">Common Questions About GlowRelief Therapy</h2><p class=\"faq-caption pp-text-base\">Clear answers to help you start safe, confident, and comfortable at home.</p></div><details class=\"faq-item\"><summary><span class=\"faq-q pp-font-semibold pp-text-base\">Is the cupping painful for beginners?</span><svg class=\"faq-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 256 256\"><path d=\"M216.49,104.49l-80,80a12,12,0,0,1-17,0l-80-80a12,12,0,0,1,17-17L128,159l71.51-71.52a12,12,0,0,1,17,17Z\"></path></svg></summary><p class=\"faq-answer pp-text-base\">No. The adjustable suction and one-button release let you start low and remove cups easily, preventing pain. Test lower levels and increase when comfortable for gentle, effective therapy.</p></details><details class=\"faq-item\"><summary><span class=\"faq-q pp-font-semibold pp-text-base\">How long does a typical session last?</span><svg class=\"faq-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 256 256\"><path d=\"M216.49,104.49l-80,80a12,12,0,0,1-17,0l-80-80a12,12,0,0,1,17-17L128,159l71.51-71.52a12,12,0,0,1,17,17Z\"></path></svg></summary><p class=\"faq-answer pp-text-base\">Most users find 15–20 minutes per session to be optimal. You can use GlowRelief daily or several times per week depending on your needs.</p></details><details class=\"faq-item\"><summary><span class=\"faq-q pp-font-semibold pp-text-base\">Can I use it on sensitive skin?</span><svg class=\"faq-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 256 256\"><path d=\"M216.49,104.49l-80,80a12,12,0,0,1-17,0l-80-80a12,12,0,0,1,17-17L128,159l71.51-71.52a12,12,0,0,1,17,17Z\"></path></svg></summary><p class=\"faq-answer pp-text-base\">Yes, the lower heat and suction settings are suitable for sensitive skin. We recommend starting on the lowest setting and testing on a small area first.</p></details><details class=\"faq-item\"><summary><span class=\"faq-q pp-font-semibold pp-text-base\">How do red light and heat help?</span><svg class=\"faq-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 256 256\"><path d=\"M216.49,104.49l-80,80a12,12,0,0,1-17,0l-80-80a12,12,0,0,1,17-17L128,159l71.51-71.52a12,12,0,0,1,17,17Z\"></path></svg></summary><p class=\"faq-answer pp-text-base\">Red light therapy penetrates deep into muscle tissue to stimulate healing at the cellular level, while heat relaxes muscle fibers and improves blood flow — together they deliver faster and more complete relief.</p></details><details class=\"faq-item\"><summary><span class=\"faq-q pp-font-semibold pp-text-base\">How long does the battery last between charges?</span><svg class=\"faq-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 256 256\"><path d=\"M216.49,104.49l-80,80a12,12,0,0,1-17,0l-80-80a12,12,0,0,1,17-17L128,159l71.51-71.52a12,12,0,0,1,17,17Z\"></path></svg></summary><p class=\"faq-answer pp-text-base\">The built-in battery provides approximately 2 hours of continuous use on a full charge. It recharges fully via USB-C in about 2 hours.</p></details><div class=\"faq-cta\"><a class=\"faq-btn pp-font-semibold\" href=\"#ProductSubmitButton-template--27477874868507__main\">Get Mine Now</a></div></div>",
        "color_scheme": "background-1",
        "padding_top": 36,
        "padding_bottom": 36
      }
    },
